If you collect 4 hidden Secret Scrolls of Cherry Blossom from somewhere in {C=0xFF016295/} Arcade mode (F1) [Haruka's Sushi Restaurant]{C=0xFF016295/}, she will make you a new 'Cherry Blossom accessory'.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
