Go to {C=0xFF016295/}Haruka's Sushi Restaurant [Arcade Mode(F1)]{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to obtain {C=0xFF016295/}15 Fresh Cherry Blossom Leaves{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and give them to Haruka.

