{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Rudolph and Santa were trying to make a White Christmas by preparing a magical snow crystal this year. 
However Rudolph lost all the crystals. He found out that Cleaner Snowman took all the crystals and now he asks you to 'frankly speak' with the Snowman to bring back  {C=0xFF016295/}One{C=0xFF4D0D08/} of the {C=0xFF016295/} Pointy Snow Crystals {C=0xFF4D0D08/} to him.
Santa will give special rewards if everyone who helps Rudolph to gather lost crystals, so let's help him! You can find Cleaner Snowman from all maps.

