{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Hunger alert! Let's help Wookiboki fill his belly by finding {C=0xFF016295/}20 Emergency Rations{C=0xFF4D0D08/} from {C=0xFF016295/}Sharpos{C=0xFF4D0D08/} at {C=0xFF016295/}Canyon of Oblivion{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

