Port of the Winds - Equipment Merchant Crispin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Crispin lost his bag while running away from the monsters on the way to Steven Trading Port.
He thinks he left his {C=0xFF016295/}bag{C=0xFF4D0D08/} at {C=0xFF016295/}Steven Trading Port [Chaos Mode(F2)] Alvida{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Help him find his belongings!

