Canyon of Oblivion - Pet Merchant Iona

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Find the best materials for pet clothing and bring them to Iona. Collect 20 Raccoon Tails and 20 Leather belts from Sharpos in  {C=0xFF016295/}Canyon of Oblivion{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Canyon of Oblivion (Mission Mode) - 10 Mushrooms

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Canyon of Oblivion - Pet Merchant Iona

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Iona wants to help her sister in Port of the Winds by gathering mushrooms, an ingredient for pet's cold medicine.  {C=0xFF016295/}Mushroom{C=0xFF4D0D08/} can be found at {C=0xFF016295/} Canyon of Oblivion Mission Map{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Meet Daisy

