Port of the Winds - General Merchant Daisy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
A new kind of medicine needs to be created in order to cure the pets. Find Daisy and ask for her help.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Catch 5 Blue Scrappies, 5 Plunger Raccoons and 5 Sharpos

