Port of the Winds - Pet Merchant Amy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Observe monsters around the Canyon of Oblivion for Amy's pet experiment. According to her, you should be able to find {C=0xFF016295/}Blue Scrappies in the Canyon of Oblivion Mission Map. Plunger Raccoons and Sharpos in the Field Map.{C=0xFF4D0D08/}

