Canyon of Oblivion - Iona

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Iona wants to help her sister's research. Find {C=0xFF016295/}Dragon Claw{C=0xFF4D0D08/} from monsters of {C=0xFF016295/}Wailing Hill{C=0xFF4D0D08/}

