Port of the Winds - General Merchant Daisy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
You have to get 15 Thorn Shells from Razor Crabbies at Jigsaw Pincers Coast, so Daisy can brew the pet medicine.

