{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Meet Don Morgan 

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Victor 

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
If you want to get the character card, visit Village Chief Don Morgan and get his signature!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Bearded Whale Coast [Mission Mode(F1)] - 5 pieces of Torn Deed

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Real Estate Agent James

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Recently Crispin was defrauded by a local Real Estate Agent. James' reputation as a real estate agent has been tarnished by this, so he wants to help Crispin get the deed of his house back.
{C=0xFF016295/}(Tip: Mission Map - Enter the Mission Maps and search through the boxes along the pier.){C=0xFF4D0D08/}

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Eradicate Captain Hookah

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Steven Trading Port - Guard Sigin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
No one seems to know about the witch that Sanka and Kunka unfortunately ran into.
The only hope rests now on {C=0xFF016295/}Captain Hookah{C=0xFF4D0D08/} who seems to know a lot about what's going on.

Hookah can be found on a{C=0xFF016295/} dock in Bearded Whale Coast (Scenario Mission Map){C=0xFF4D0D08/} committing crimes.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Slay 20 monsters at the Bearded Whale Coast

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Victor

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
In order to enter Port of the Winds armed, we need to obtain a pass. As a test of skill, Victor wants 20 monsters slain at the Bearded Whale Coast.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Send out the survey to Jeremy, Davy, Daisy, Rony and Crispin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Traitor's Ridge - Mercenary Thomas

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Mercenary Thomas has a peculiar hobby. He's trying to figure out who is the fairest in Port of the Winds. Deliver the survey to Jeremy, Davy, Daisy, Rony and Crispin.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Stop Alvida

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Steven Trading Port - Guard Sigin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
{C=0xFF016295/}Alvida{C=0xFF4D0D08/} is supposedly placing a bomb to destroy Beach Attack and the surrounding areas.
Let's stop her and report to Colin.
Alvida can be found inside{C=0xFF016295/} the cave next to Sigin (Scenario Mission Map){C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Meet Vincent 

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Vincent 

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
In order to make character card, you should meet with Vincent the Butler in Port of the Winds. 
Answering some of the simple question from Vincent, you will get the card from him.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Answer Vincent's Questions

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Wind - Vincent

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
In order to make a character card, you should answer Vincent's question correctly.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver a gift to Cindy for Thomas

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Veteran Thief Cindy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
It was decided by Thomas that Cindy is the prettiest woman in Port of the Winds.
Victor wants to reward her for that with honor. Please pass reward to {C=0xFF016295/}Cyndi {C=0xFF4D0D08/}on behalf of Victor.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Speak with Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The guard captain must be {C=0xFF016295/}Colin{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Let's go to {C=0xFF016295/}Port of the Winds{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and ask Colin about Farrell.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Meet Thomas

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Victor

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Cindy decided to deliver a warning to Thomas for his actions.
Deliver the warning message to Thomas.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Investigate Nautilus Port

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Find out what is causing the stench by having a look around Nautilus Port then report back to Colin.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Steven Trading Port - Get 20 monster corpses

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The reason behind the bad smell is the dead monsters.
Bring 20 monster corpses from Steven Trading Port.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Bearded Whale Coast -  Collect Thomas's Sword

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Victor

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Find {C=0xFF016295/}Thomas's Sword at Bearded Whale Coast {C=0xFF4D0D08/}and bring that to Victor, in Love.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat Farrell [Enter after getting the 5 keys in the City Hall Sewer]

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Lord Steven Jr.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
All preparations have been made. Defeat Dr. Farrell and put a halt to his deranged experiments! To enter his laboratory, you will need to gather all 5 keys from the monsters in his mansion. Please make sure to prepare your {C=0xFF016295/}Gas Mask{C=0xFF4D0D08/} before you get in. Otherwise your HP will drain.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Deliver Thomas's Sword to Cyndi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Thief Class Master Cyndi 

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver Thomas's Sword to {C=0xFF016295/}Cyndi{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and impress her.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Let's hand Farrell's diary to Larell at Moonlight Shore Village

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Larell

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
You have been recognized as a fellowship member by Sovereign Steven Jr.
You must therefore fulfil your duties! Let's meet the great magician Pablo at Libra and give him Farrell's diary.
(Libra is for level 30, so make sure you are ready.)

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Bearded Whale Coast - Collect 20 Starry Corpse

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Thief Class Master Cyndi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Out of the blue, Cyndi asked you to {C=0xFF016295/}collect 20 Starry Corpse at Bearded Whale Coast{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Grant her requests.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Bring the Sword to Victor

