{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Show Approval document of Dragon Fellowship to Class master Edeline.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Colin said that Dragon Fellowship's test is just fighting on the battlefield. So he sent us here to resolve the wolves' issue. So I came here with Approval document of Dragon Fellowship and met {C=0xFF016295/}Class master Edeline{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in this village.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect 20 Mutant monster's Fluid in the Bearded Whale Coast.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Class master Edeline heard a rumor from tourists and made a decision to slay the leader of the wolves. Edeline said that if we made a vaccine, we can solve the wolves' issue, so she requested to have {C=0xFF016295/}20 Mutant monster's Fluid{C=0xFF4D0D08/} from {C=0xFF016295/}Starry and Crabby{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in the {C=0xFF016295/}Bearded Whale Coast{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

