Giving a Mutant report to Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Edeline has finished the analyze of the Mutant monster's Fluid. Let's go to{C=0xFF016295/}Colin{C=0xFF4D0D08/}with this Mutant report.

