{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Blacksmith Davi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Coin said that investigating Farrell's lab wouldn't be possible, so he gave me a search warrant for the water tank of Culvert instead of his lab. But now there will be many difficulties in the water tank of the City Hall Sewer, especially when it comes to breathing. So let's go to {C=0xFF016295/}Blacksmith Davi{C=0xFF4D0D08/} with an Order for a Gas Mask and ask{C=0xFF016295/} him how to make a Gas Mask{C=0xFF4D0D08/}

