Port of the Winds - Davi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Let's collect {C=0xFF016295/}5 Sharp Blades{C=0xFF4D0D08/}and {C=0xFF016295/}5 Piece of Clothes{C=0xFF4D0D08/}from the {C=0xFF016295/}Sharpo monster{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, {C=0xFF016295/}Canyon of Oblivion{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

