{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Let's get into the City Hall Sewer, destroy the water tank, and get 5 Samples of Mutant tentacles.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
You didn't know what you were supposed to find, but Edeline told you what to get. She said there will be a water tank in the City Hall Sewer. Let's get into the {C=0xFF016295/}City Hall Sewer{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, destroy a {C=0xFF016295/}water tank{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, and get {C=0xFF016295/}5 Samples of Mutant Tentacles{C=0xFF4D0D08/} then report to Colin!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Give a Sample of Mutant tentacles to Edeline.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Finally I got Sample of Mutant tentacles. If I give this sample to {C=0xFF016295/}Edeline{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, she can make a vaccine after she analyzes it.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect 5 soul.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
After analyzing Edeline's mutant sample, Dr. Farrell's research is about a chemical to re-organise creature's molecules. Edeline said that she is able to make a vaccine with Dr.Farrell's Sample of Mutant tentacles. For this job, Edeline needs {C=0xFF016295/}5 souls{C=0xFF4D0D08/} for enhancing its magical power. Soul can be generated from {C=0xFFFF0000/}equipment dismantling{C=0xFF4D0D08/} so please {C=0xFFFF0000/}collect{C=0xFF4D0D08/} soul from it.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Let's go to Wolves' Den in the Wailing Hill and pour a vaccine on the wolf that walks on two legs.

