Port of the Winds - Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Vaccines have finally been made. We just pour this vaccines to the wolf with both legs. According to the guard, Wolves' Den is located near Wailing Hill, so let's go to {C=0xFF016295/}Wailing Hill{C=0xFF4D0D08/} now.

