{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Colin has changed his mind after he read Edeline's Reference in regards to Dr. Farrell. Colin wants you to search {C=0xFF016295/}Dr. Farrell's Research Lab{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in the {C=0xFF016295/}City Hall Sewer{C=0xFF4D0D08/}  and make {C=0xFF016295/}Dr. Farrell{C=0xFF4D0D08/} stop! (According to the city's plans of Dr. Farrell's research lab, without {C=0xFF016295/}5 keys{C=0xFF4D0D08/} you can't enter his lab.)

Okay... look at this...
{C=0xFF016295/}... (skip) according to the witness' testimony... Dr. Farrell has been successful in clinical demonstrations. ...{C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Wha.. What? His clinical demonstration has succeeded!?%%

