{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of Winds - Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Colin found out that there are Red Gemstones in Dr. Farrell's Lab. They hold a tremendous amount of power after they have been purified! Colin wants to have {C=0xFF016295/}1 Dr. Farrell's Gemstone{C=0xFF4D0D08/} so he can create a {C=0xFF016295/}Mysterious Dr. Farrell's Gemstone{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.So, let's bring him 1 Dr. Farrell's Gemstones.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Let's find someone whos seen a seagull in the Bearded Whale Coast.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Bearded Whale Coast - Jess

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
A seagull stole the diary from Colin. The seagull has flown over to Bearded Whale Coast directly, so let's go to {C=0xFF016295/}Bearded Whale Coast{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and find the seagull. If we can't find any, we need to find {C=0xFF016295/}someone who has seen a seagull{C=0xFF4D0D08/} at least.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
