{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
According to Jess, Hookha's Seagull pet stole Dr.Farrell's book from Colin. The whole thing could have been planned by Captain Hookah. Anyway, let's go to {C=0xFF016295/}Colin{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and report this to him.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Slay Captain Hookah at the Bearded Whale Coast's scenario mode.

