Port of the Winds - Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Colin ordered me to get int Captain Hookah's Villa in the {C=0xFF016295/}Mission's scenario mode{C=0xFF4D0D08/}at the {C=0xFF016295/}Bearded Whale Coast{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and {C=0xFF016295/}slay Captain Hookah{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and get back Dr. Farrell's diary again.

