Colin decided to wipe the pirates out. He will follow me with hte Dragon Fellowship soon, so he ordered me to go to {C=0xFF016295/}Steven Trading Port{C=0xFF4D0D08/} first and contact {C=0xFF016295/}Sijin{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Taking Dr. Farrell's diary from Alvida and disarming bombs at the scenario mode mission in Steven Trading Port.

