Steven Trading Port - Sijin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Alvida placed bombs around their place and they got Dr. Farrell's diary. If the Dragon Fellowship arrive there without warning, there will be a huge disaster! Let's get in{C=0xFF016295/}Mission's scenario mode{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in the  {C=0xFF016295/}Steven Trading Port{C=0xFF4D0D08/}and {C=0xFF016295/}disarming the bombs{C=0xFF4D0D08/} along with taking {C=0xFF016295/} Dr. Farrell's diary {C=0xFF4D0D08/}from Alvida!!!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
