Port of the Winds - Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
I finally slayed Alvida and brought back Dr. Farrell's diary. Sijin wanted to {C=0xFF016295/}report it to Colin{C=0xFF4D0D08/}in the Port of the Winds

