{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
I told my story in Steven Trading Port to Colin. And it seemed to touch his heart. So Colin tried to talk about it to the Lord {C=0xFF016295/}Steven Jr.{C=0xFF4D0D08/} about my service and contribution.

