{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Libra - Equipment merchant Dwayne

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dwayne seems to have a lot of interest in what happened to Dr. Farrell. That's probably because of General Blood's Armour which can be used for high quality equipment. But he doesn't want to admit that. In any case, it seems helping him will bring some information so head out to the  {C=0xFF016295/}Sanctuaries and Valid Raeth{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and slay monsters to see if you can gain something from them.

