So there is a story between Turner, Adelio and Herna. Helping out now may prove to be useful later on when searching for information about Lavalon.
{C=0xFF016295/}Marks of Fire{C=0xFF4D0D08/} can be found in the {C=0xFF016295/}Valid Raeth{C=0xFF4D0D08/} from those  {C=0xFF016295/}Lava Boombooms{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

