Libra - Captain of Guard Hoffman

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
All the villagers of Libra got weak and sick because of continuous darkness. 
Captain of Guard is guessing the slay the monsters around Scalding Swamps and undo the black magic curse will return everything to normal. As he requested, go to Scalding Swamps and slay 30 Firefly Priests.

