{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Get 30 Spider Shells and 40 Squirrel poops

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pine Cone Hill - Shaman Orhah

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Shaman Orhah have problem looking into the Verdurous Forest. She needs a vision enhancement medicine. It can be made by mixing {C=0xFF016295/}30 Spider Shells{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and {C=0xFF016295/}40 Squirrel poops{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Let's find them and bring to Orhah. Each can be found in {C=0xFF016295/}Grass Wind Hills and Pine Cone Hill{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

