Conversation with Hel Krouzer after the forest is purified.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Verdurous Forest - Hel Krouzer

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Mutisha left through a magical portal saying she will wake the Ancient Golem Aram. Hel Krouzer will chase after Mutisha. Let's purify the forest using the ring that is given to us.

