Gods' Sanctuary - Hel Krouzer

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Hel Krouzer will follow Mutisha to {C=0xFF016295/}Kundara{C=0xFF4D0D08/} where {C=0xFF016295/}Ancient Golem Aram{C=0xFF4D0D08/} is sleeping. Hel Krouzer will go to {C=0xFF016295/}Gods' Sanctuary{C=0xFF4D0D08/} so let's look for {C=0xFF016295/}Hel Krouzer{C=0xFF4D0D08/} there.

