{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat 100 monsters at the Verdurous Forest

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pine Cone Hills - Naoi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Message was delivered to Mika Tribe as Rudaella, however Mike Tribe do not have spare hand because of Woodsman Burnaun. Naoi want the Dragon Fellowship to defeat the monsters. Enter {C=0xFF016295/}the Verdurous Forest{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and defeat {C=0xFF016295/}100 monsters{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to purify the Verdurous Forest!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Enter the Verdurous Forest and defeat Thorn Tree Spirit, Poisonous Tree Spirit, Rotten Tree Spirit

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pine Cone Hills - Shaman Orhah

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Orhah is asking to cut polluted tree before all the trees in the Verdurous Forest trees get polluted. Enter {C=0xFF016295/}the Verdurous Forest{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and defeat {C=0xFF016295/}Thorn Tree Spirit, Poisonous Tree Spirit, Rotten Tree Spirit{C=0xFF4D0D08/} before it is too late.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Conversation is Blacksmith Rugor at Pine Cone Hills

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pine Cone Hills - Blacksmith Rugor

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Naoi talks about Mist Elf Armour, that has been developed in a very special way. She told the Fellowship to find and talk to {C=0xFF016295/}Blacksmith Rugor{C=0xFF4D0D08/} if the Fellowship wants to know about Mist Elf Armour.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Enter the Verdurous Forest and collect the 200 fog glues

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pine Cone Hills - Rugor

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Rugor says to put together a Mist Elf Armour, a special ingredient is required. The special ingredient is the Fog glue, and it can be obtained only at the Verdurous Forest. If you want Mist Elf Armour, enter {C=0xFF016295/}the Verdurous Forest{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and collect {C=0xFF016295/}200 fog glue.{C=0xFF4D0D08/}

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Enter the Verdurous Forest and collect each of Mist Elf Helmet's Left, Right, Front, Rear, Top piece.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pine Cone Hills - Rugor

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Rugor claims he can make a Mist Elf Armour if all the parts are ready. Let's try with Helmet first! Enter the Verdurous Forest and collect {C=0xFF016295/}each of Mist Elf Helmet's Left, Right, Front, Rear, Top piece {C=0xFF4D0D08/}and Rugor will make the Helmet for you.

