{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Forgotten Village - Gallia

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
There is something written about a dragon on the tablets but it's difficult to decipher because it is very old and needs a lot of restoration work using a great deal of magical skill. In order to repair the tablets you need to head to {C=0xFF016295/}Forgotten Village Mission mode and slay Mimir Kahunas{C=0xFF4D0D08/}until you find {C=0xFF016295/}40 Soulstones{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

