Detective Gordon

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Sharmaan, a man of Kentarous betrayed his general and gone. If he went to an evil tribe called Kentarous, he might be killed by Karkharous. Let's go to Gods' Sanctuary and clear [Arcade Mode F1] and tell Detective Gordon.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
50 Sticky Pine Needles

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pine Cone Hills - Naoi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect 50 Sticky Pine Niddles as a second mission to return Naoi's prescience.
Defeat flying squirrels around Pine Cone Hills will produce them.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect 40 Pine Resin Marbles

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pine Cone Hills - Rugor

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collecting 40 Pine Resin Marbles is the third task required to return Naoi's prescience.
Collect pine resin marbles by defeating flying squirrels around Pine Cone Hills.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
