Fungoid Village - Ringo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
You barely got your hands on the Snake Flower Cane, but it was too late. Grania is now imprisoned there for 80 years. She says she has a letter for Ringo. {C=0xFF016295/}Let's get the letter to Ringo{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

