To gain the Fungoid Village's trust, you need to help them reconstruct their village.
This time, the work is to supply food to the villagers.
Go to  {C=0xFF016295/}Tutu Tree Forest or Ruined Mushroom Factory{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and slay  {C=0xFF016295/}Toenail Wing Kindsman{C=0xFF4D0D08/} monsters to get Royal Jellies.

