Arka

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
There is a Fairy named Arka that's like a queen to the fairies that rule this area.
Let's {C=0xFF016295/}Eradicate Arka{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, who kidnaps children to make them share her dreams!
She should be hiding in the farthest southwest area (Scenario Mode F5).%%

