Scenario Mode F5 Mode - Eradicate Bubobubo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Chief Fungarf

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
There is a legend in the Mimir tribe about {C=0xFF016295/}Bubobubo{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.
And one day an owl showed up and started to serve up the Fungoid tribe as sacrifices to Bubobubo. . .
Let's help the Fungoid tribe by eradicating the Bubobubo.
Bubobubo can be found at  {C=0xFF016295/} some hideout of the Mimir tribe in the Forgotten Village(Scenario Mode F5) {C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

