Let the humans know that the Fungoid Tribe have resolved their hostility towards humans! Deliver the letter that Chief Massirun wrote to {C=0xFF016295/}Sovereign Steven the second{C=0xFF4D0D08/}  at Port of the Winds by using  {C=0xFF016295/}Port of the Winds Return Scroll{C=0xFF4D0D08/} .

