{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Mosanra

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The Fungoid Chief Fungarf is 532 years old this year. He seems to be suffering from neuralgia.
Let's get him 20 Green and BlueVegetable Oil Clots, which are known remedies for the Fungoids.
Head to Forgotten Village and slay the{C=0xFF016295/}Evil Flowers{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to get some.

