Fungoid Village - Sanson the Blacksmith

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
It turns out that a Dragon passed through here and destroyed the roads. And the only way now is the door that's been infested by worms. Let's take the portal on the right and go to Forgotten Village and {C=0xFF016295/}Slay 50 Worms{C=0xFF4D0D08/} then return to Sanson.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Forgotten Village - 40 Horned Worms Skins

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Blacksmith Sanson

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Another Dragon attack will devastate the Fungoid village. Missontun the Blacksmith says they need to make a lot of armour to defend the village. Let's help him by getting {C=0xFF016295/}40 Horned Worm Skins{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

