Someone from the Fungoid Village

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Chris from the Port of the Winds has been having a hard time because the food doesn't agree with him here. He says there is a {C=0xFF016295/}Master Chef {C=0xFF4D0D08/}somewhere around Fungoid Village.
Let's find the chef!

