Get 40 Fur Herbs

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Mosanra the Innkeep

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
It turns out that the master chef was Mosanra the Innkeep. But Mosanra says she lost her sense of taste and needs {C=0xFF016295/}15 Fur Herbs{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to recover it.
The herbs can be found in {C=0xFF016295/}Tutu Tree Forest, from Dryads{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

I won't expect much
But... If I can have my sense of taste back, I'll cook the best Pufferfish Dish.
You can find Fur Herbs by slaying {C=0xFF016295/}Dryads in Tutu Tree Forest{C=0xFF4D0D08/}

