Mosanra is excited about being able to cook again. She's asked you to get her some ingredients. Let's get her {C=0xFF016295/}20 Puffer Fins and 20 Puffer Tails{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. The Puffers are around Tutu Tree Forest.

