{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The dish is finally finished! Now, let's get this to {C=0xFF016295/}Chris the Guard{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.
