One of Chris' fellow guards was attacked by a Mimir Poison Needle Soldier and was severely poisoned. We must find {C=0xFF016295/}20 Plant Poisons{C=0xFF4D0D08/} for the antidote! They can be found from  {C=0xFF016295/}Dryads{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

