Gallia has heard that there is a Flower of life growing in the Land of temptation. She asked you to find out if it's true.
Let's investigate this {C=0xFF016295/}Flower of life in the Land of Temptation{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Frigid Canyon investigation

