Fungoid Village - Warrior Commander Dean

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dean is looking for the source or witness of the rumours about the flying objects.
The rumours started at {C=0xFFFF5917/}Frigid Canyon{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Let's investigate!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Forgotten Village [Mission Mode] - 50 Mimir Poison Needle Soldiers.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Chris the Guard

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Sigma was safely treated and is recovering. But the Mimir Poison Needle Soldiers cannot be forgiven for this.Slay 50 {C=0xFF016295/}Mimir Poison Needle Soldiers {C=0xFF4D0D08/}and talk to Chris.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Find Mosanra's Necklace Bead - Forgotten Village [Mission Mode]

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Mosanra the Innkeeper

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
You found Mosanra's necklace, but it's broken. She wants you to find the rest of the Beads. If the Porkies have one part of the necklace, {C=0xFF016295/}Uncle Porky or other Porkies{C=0xFF4D0D08/} should have the other two...

