{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Ponga doesn't know what this herb is either. Let's get this to {C=0xFF016295/}Fungoid Village Chief Fungarf{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

