Meet Baron the Dark Magician

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Village of Ash Mist - Baron the Dark Magician

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Spooky has no clue where and how to get the materials. Luckily, Spooky saw {C=0xFF016295/}Baron the Dark Magician{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in the Village of Ash Mist. Let's show the list to him.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect 25 pieces of Toa Mello's Leather and 25 Toa Mello Horns at Frost Lake

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Forgotten Village (or the Village of Slumber) - Gallia the Forest Watch

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Bring {C=0xFF016295/}25 Toa Mello's Leather{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and {C=0xFFFF5917/}25 Toa Mello's Horn{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to {C=0xFF00863C/}Gallia{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in {C=0xFF016295/}Fungoid Village{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to show her what effects the Flower of life is causing...

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Storm Snowfield - Slay 50 Yeti Angakoqs

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Warrior Commander Dean

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
There seems to be a certain area where the flying objects appear, and now someone must stand watch to find out what they are. However, the area is infested with monsters and must be cleared out. {C=0xFF016295/}Slay 50 Yeti Angakoqs in the Storm Snowfield{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and go back to Warrior Commander Dean.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver a letter to Tod in Village of Ash Mist

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Village of Ash Mist - Tod, Soldier

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}Quest Details{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Cris asked to you to deliver a letter to Tod in Village of Ash Mist.
To get to Village of Ash Mist will not be easy. Prepare well and find Tod.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Get 40 Devil's Grass

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Chief Fungarf

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungarf says that this herb is called Devil's Grass. This grass contains a strong poison that is very contagious. Fungarf believes that this has to do with the Dragon passing through. Let's go to {C=0xFF016295/}Pococo Garden and slay all the monsters until you can get 40 Devil's Grass{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, before the poison spreads.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Meet Gordon the Detective

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Village of Ash Mist - Gordon the Detective

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Upon reading the reports, Warrior Commander Dean says the one of the rumors reported is very exact and detailed.
He says the person is not a Fungoid or human but a wandering human. His name is  {C=0xFF016295/}Matthew{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. As his whereabouts is unknown, let's find {C=0xFF016295/}Gordon the Detective{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in {C=0xFF016295/}Village of Ash Mist{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to ask about where Matthew is..

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Village of Slumber - Get 40 Sticky Fluids

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Mosanra the Innkeep

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Mosanra has asked you to get some sticky liquids to fix her necklace. Go to the {C=0xFF016295/}Village of Slumber{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and get 40 Sticky Fluids from {C=0xFF016295/}Evil Seed Flowers and Moths{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, then talk to Mosanra.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Get 40 Moth Wings

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Blacksmith Sanson

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Sanson the Blacksmith has requested you to find some materials for a vaccine. Get {C=0xFF016295/}40 Moth Wings{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and talk to Sanson. they can be found from  {C=0xFF016295/}Moths{C=0xFF4D0D08/} at the {C=0xFF016295/} Village of Slumber{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Slay 100 monsters in the Land of Temptation

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village/Village of Slumber - Gallia the Forest Watch

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The monsters around the Flower of Life is diminishing it's effect. Let's head to 
the{C=0xFF016295/}Land of Temptation and slay 100 monsters{C=0xFF4D0D08/}and then talk to Gallia the forest Watch.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Conversation with Fungarf

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Fungarf

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
After research, we found that the effect of that flower is just what we expected. But we also found out that if we keep those monsters live there, it could get dangerous.
We need to let our chief know about it.
Let's give this news to {C=0xFF016295/}Chief Fungarf{C=0xFF4D0D08/}

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Village of Slumber [Chaos Mode F2] - Defeat 100 Mimir Monsters

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Village of Slumber - Baron

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Baron the Dark Magician seems to know about this contamination that Fungarf spoke of. A big tree at the Village of SLumber releases some kind of steam as it bears fruit, but someone has been putting poison in the steam. This will cause many casualties, but we can help stop it by slaying {C=0xFF016295/}100 Mimirs{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Village of Slumber Mission Mode - Find Town Safe

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Camilla the Banker

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
After the incident, Camilla the Banker ran away with the Safe.
But when she awoke she was home and the safe was gone.
She doesn't remember who took it, but she does remember that {C=0xFF016295/}it was a human-looking monster who was short and carrying a weapon{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. 
Let's make sure we find it for the people of the village!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Village of Slumber [Chaos Mode(F2)] Hard(F3) - Find Camilla's Note

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Camilla the banker

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Camilla found the safe but can't remember the combination due to the head injury. She says she hid a note in {C=0xFF016295/}the Village of Slumber [Chaos Mode(F2)] Hard(F3){C=0xFF4D0D08/} with the combination written on it. But there are a lot of monsters there and it might be hard to get it back. Let's get to the end point of Village of Slumber [Chaos Mode(F2)] Hard(F3) and find {C=0xFF016295/}Camilla's Note{C=0xFF4D0D08/} for her.

