Information about the Black Witch has finally been revealed to Hel Krouzer and he is now investigating the movements of the Dragon Fellowship. Hel Krouzer will give you the information if you prove yourself to him.
Hel Krouzer has given you two options, you can either prove yourself through PvP or through PvE. Speak to {C=0xFFFF5917/}Hel Krouzer{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in {C=0xFF016295/}Vartika Hill{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and choose your path.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
